lead_paragraph: Former U.S. women's soccer star Abby Wambach pleaded not guilty on Tuesday to driving under the influence of alcohol and was given permission by an Oregon judge to travel out of the state for work reasons, prosecutors said.

headline.print_headline: U.S. Women's Soccer Star Wambach Pleads Innocent to Drunk Driving Charge
